snippet.title: Cuphead E3 2015 Trailer for Xbox One
snippet.description:
A single player or co-op "run and gun" platformer, heavily focused on boss battles. Inspired by 1930s cartoons, the visuals are hand drawn and inked and the music is all original jazz recordings. Xbox One Console exclusive.  

For more information, please visit www.xbox.com/E3
